            . I am a porter at the <placeName id="t18130714-12-crimeloc65">Bull-inn, Friday-street, Cheapside</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18130714-12-crimeloc65" type="placeName" value="Bull-inn, Friday-street, Cheapside"></interp>
