                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18130714-12-off63 t18130714-12-crimeloc65"></join>. The Axminster waggon inns there. The Axminster waggon arrived on Friday night; on Saturday morning I saw this tub of butter in 
               <persName id="t18130714-12-person169">
                  Robert 
                  Russell
               <interp inst="t18130714-12-person169" type="surname" value="Russell"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18130714-12-person169" type="given" value="Robert"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18130714-12-person169" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
